 attachment to money, time, and talent.

276
00:23:54,980 --> 00:24:03,900
 >> [FOREIGN]

277
00:24:03,900 --> 00:24:07,180
 >> We are stingy because we have forgotten that breathing,

278
00:24:07,180 --> 00:24:10,300
 relationship, and talents are all give from God.

279
00:24:10,300 --> 00:24:19,260
 >> [FOREIGN]

280
00:24:19,260 --> 00:24:23,940
 >> Jesus knew that people's heart were filled with an attachment to power,

281
00:24:23,940 --> 00:24:24,980
 money, and time.

282
00:24:24,980 --> 00:24:32,980
 >> [FOREIGN]

283
00:24:34,620 --> 00:24:40,220
 >> He drove cattle and sheep away to remind us to let go of those attachments and

284
00:24:40,220 --> 00:24:42,580
 return ownership to God.

